    <item>
      <title>印度财富管理公司 360 One 计划在增长动力中成立新基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/india-s-wealth-manager-360-one-plans-new-fund-amid-growth-drive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最大的财富管理公司之一正利用印度的自由市场避风港，计划在那里设立一只 2 亿美元的基金，由投资者 Ruchir Sharma 管理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/india-s-wealth-manager-360-one-plans-new-fund-amid-growth-drive</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 06:24:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国审计法院称与欧盟的赤字差距不可接受</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/french-audit-court-says-deficit-gap-versus-eu-is-unacceptable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国国家审计院表示，与其他欧盟国家相比，预算赤字的差距是不可接受的，下一届政府需要一个连贯可信的计划来修复公共财政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/french-audit-court-says-deficit-gap-versus-eu-is-unacceptable</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 06:15:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯沃琪集团利润因中国需求疲软暴跌 70%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/swatch-group-profit-falls-on-weak-china-strong-swiss-franc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受中国经济放缓影响，瑞士钟表制造商和其他奢侈品公司斯沃琪集团的销售额和利润大幅下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/swatch-group-profit-falls-on-weak-china-strong-swiss-franc</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 05:38:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行称外国银行正在抢购短期印度债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/foreign-banks-are-snapping-up-short-term-indian-bonds-bofa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行印度固定收益部门主管表示，全球各大银行在购买印度主权债券时，都瞄准较短的期限，以期在供应有限的情况下提高流动性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/foreign-banks-are-snapping-up-short-term-indian-bonds-bofa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 01:14:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普枪击事件后，油价波动，美元走强成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普遭遇暗杀，且中国十一届三中全会于周一开幕，油价因此波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 23:29:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：特朗普押注导致美元上涨、美国国债下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-futures-waver-as-traders-juggle-trump-win-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在遭遇暗杀后，投资者加大对唐纳德·特朗普将赢得美国总统大选的押注，导致美元上涨，美国国债下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-futures-waver-as-traders-juggle-trump-win-bets-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 22:18:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球市场在反弹后“特朗普交易”增多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/global-markets-ramp-up-the-trump-trade-after-rally-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普遇刺未遂之后，随着世界金融市场重新开放，有一件事似乎是可能的：特朗普的交易将获得更大的动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/global-markets-ramp-up-the-trump-trade-after-rally-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
